7 p.m. karaoke at Yangtze Restaurant, 509 High St, Somersworth, NH
7 p.m. dancing then karaoke at 3 Continental Blvd, Rochester, NH
9 p.m. live music, Dover Brick House, 2 Orchard Street, Dover, NH
9 p.m. live music, Kelleyâ€™s Row, 421 Central Ave, Dover, NH

We hope to see you there! Trying new food and then dancing & listening to music sounds like a great night.
